{"tid":2067441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武肺致糧荒 自製危機逼減制裁","createTime":"2020-06-17T04:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T04:15:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3be76b903b6dab592fc514f97357791864c199d1","tid":2067441,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200617/XCB5DMTLOLZ6FQ3S77RFGUEUAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2FXCB5DMTLOLZ6FQ3S77RFGUEUAE%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=dabe263d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200617%2FXCB5DMTLOLZ6FQ3S77RFGUEUAE%2F&h=b3a3cda2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200617/XCB5DMTLOLZ6FQ3S77RFGUEUAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n武肺致糧荒 自製危機逼減制裁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WXCCGFT5X2PYMBUYURIEUZ3WWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWXCCGFT5X2PYMBUYURIEUZ3WWY.gif&h=0bcc0cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓揚言在非軍事區重新駐兵，南韓K55坦克於邊境佈防。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】<br />\n<br />\n北韓近期突然以強硬態度應對南韓，昨日更乾脆炸毀兩國的聯絡辦公室，原因很可能是該國經濟因武漢肺炎疫情大受打擊，急需製造危機局面迫使國際減輕制裁和轉移國民視線，相信指摘南韓脫北者發放反朝文宣只是發難的藉口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉移國民視線<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：啟用僅21月 作用如使館<br />\n<br />\n北韓在國際制裁下十分依賴從中國入口資源，惟該國早在1月已封鎖中朝邊境，至近期才重開，估計期間國內曾出現物資短缺，甚至糧荒。此外，北韓3月對中國的出口量按年大跌96%，有專家認為北韓對中國封關的傷害更甚於國際制裁，料金正恩不少經濟項目今年都難達標。<br />\n<br />\n面對嚴峻的經濟難題，北韓急需國際放寬制裁和得到中韓援助，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。喬治梅森大學韓國分校學者亞伯拉罕伊恩（Andray Abrahamian）亦認為金正恩是刻意引發危機局面，製造另一個能打破僵局的時刻，迫使美韓在短期內讓步。<br />\n<br />\n不過，北韓經濟雖因武。。。。。。。。。。。。。作。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日電訊報》"},{"pid":"e68efacf45b2182b3f34cdcb9b1e1317b83db2a8","tid":2067441,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"大種乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}